Package org.cougaar.core.servlet

Interface Summary
ServletUtil.ParamVisitor Simple callback API for use with "setParams(..)".
SimpleServletSupport This is a simple API for a Servlet to access COUGAAR Services, such as the Blackboard.
 

Class Summary
BaseServletComponent Abstract base-class for a Component that obtains the ServletService and registers a Servlet.
BlackboardServlet Deprecated. use ServletPlugin.
ComponentServlet Abstract base-class for a Component that is also a Servlet.
ServletFrameset Base class for serlvets that generate a per-agent data page.
ServletMultiFrameset Base class for serlvets that have multiple frames with an agent selection list.
ServletUtil Utility methods that may assist in writing Servlets.
SimpleServletComponent Component that loads a Servlet and provides the SimpleServletSupport.
SimpleServletSupportImpl This is a generic API, provided by "SimpleServletComponent", that allows a Servlet to access COUGAAR Services.
